title: EXCLUSIVE: Government Paid Millions to Vaccine-Injured Kids
description:
A group of parents are saying the Federal government has paid off multi-million dollar settlements for dozens of families whose kids suffered brain damage after receiving children vaccines.  As you know the Federal government has denied any connection between autism and vaccines, does this seem like a cover up? One parent speaks out on the autism settlement.  Dr. Coomer has her medical opinion on the subject. 

For more, go to http://www.foxnewsinsider.com.
